casebody.data:
Diandra N. WEBB
v.
Donnie HARRISON, Wake County Jail No. 166P18 Supreme Court of North Carolina. June 5, 2018 Ms. Diandra N. Webb, for Webb, Diandra N. Mr. Daniel P. O'Brien, Raleigh, Special Deputy Attorney General, for Harrison, Donnie, et al. Mr. Joseph L. Hyde, Raleigh, Assistant Attorney General

ORDER

Upon consideration of the application filed by Plaintiff on the 1st of June 2018 in this matter for Writ of Habeas Corpus, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court, Wake County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 5th of June 2018."
